## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources that predominantly present arguments against marijuana legalization. The perspectives included are primarily opinion-based and may not encompass the full spectrum of scientific research on the topic. Additionally, the report does not explore the potential benefits of marijuana legalization, which could provide a more balanced view of the issue. Further research, including peer-reviewed studies, would be necessary to provide a comprehensive analysis.